Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:18.37,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}一瞬間飛奔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:18.37,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}走り出す瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.46,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}變成了輕盈的微風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.46,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}阪道で風になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:26.38,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}曬在身上的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:26.38,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}燒きつけた陽射しが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.59,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}是胸口激揚的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.59,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}胸の奧熱くした
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:36.54,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Ah 只要能接近你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:36.54,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Ah　君に近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:39.57,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}腳步就跟著快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:39.57,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}行くたび早くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:42.61,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}穿越時空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:42.61,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}時を驅ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:49.70,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}喜歡那充滿預感的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:49.70,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}始まりの予感させる眼差しが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:53.26,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}小小的愛情就可以滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:53.26,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}小さな愛でいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:54.95,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}總是在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:54.95,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}いつも側で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.88,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}理所當然的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.88,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}あたり前の時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:03.03,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}又多了一個笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:03.03,SongJpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}また一つ增える笑い聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:06.70,SongChn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}響亮的穿透雲霄
